{"id":15409,"date":"2013-07-28T10:21:34","date_gmt":"2013-07-28T06:21:34","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=15409"},"modified":"2025-03-13T13:57:49","modified_gmt":"2025-03-13T09:57:49","slug":"allah-teaches-adam-salaam","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/allah-teaches-adam-salaam\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Salaam: Allah teaches Adam greeting of peace"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<b>Allah created Adam in His image, sixty cubits tall. When He created him, Allah said: Go and greet these groups of assembled angels with peace and listen to how they greet you, for this will be the greeting among your progeny. Adam said: Peace be upon you. The angels said: Peace be upon you and the mercy of Allah. Thus, they added the mercy of Allah. Everyone who enters Paradise will be in the image of Adam, for the creation has continued to diminish in stature until now<\/b>.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6227, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2841<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <b><i>Muttafaqun Alayhi<\/i><\/b> (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062e\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0622\u062f\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0635\u064f\u0648\u0631\u064e\u062a\u0650\u0647\u0650 \u0637\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u0647\u064f \u0633\u0650\u062a\u064f\u0651